headline: Is Federal Realty a Buy Below $100
summary: What does Federal Realty do?  Federal Realty is largely a retail landlord owning strip malls and mixed-use developments.  Unlike many of its strip mall REIT peers, which grow by adding more properties to their portfolios, Federal Realty only owns 100 or so assets.
